      "author": "abcamus",
      "description": "### ✨ New Features\n- **Grid view**: toggle between list/grid in the cloud file picker\n- **Multi-select**: check files/directories and batch insert via the footer button\n- **Lucide icons**: file type icons now use Obsidian-compatible Lucide SVGs\n- **Unified toolbar**: compact toolbar with cloud selector, breadcrumbs, search toggle and view switcher\n- **Always-visible footer**: the insert button stays pinned at the bottom of the picker\n- **Vertical cascade**: batch-inserted nodes fan out without overlapping\n\n### 🔧 Improvements\n- Cloud insert button uses `mod-draggable` class to match native card-menu buttons\n- Scrollbar always visible in file list\n- Folder icon uses manual SVG for consistent closed-folder rendering across Obsidian versions",
